# Astro config ↔ content config

- **`astro.config.mjs`:** Defines `site`, Vite + Tailwind plugin, Markdown/Shiki options, integrations (`sitemap`, `mdx`). Changing `site` affects RSS (`context.site`), sitemap, and absolute URLs — update SEO placeholders in `src/components/fundations/head/Seo.astro` when going live.
- **`src/content.config.ts`:** Defines collections and Zod schemas. Any schema change must be coordinated with:
  - All `getCollection(...)` / `render(...)` usages under `src/pages/` and layouts
  - `src/pages/rss.xml.js` (only serializes `posts` fields today)
- **Prefer minimal edits:** Do not add integrations or npm dependencies unless the user requests it and `package.json` is updated.
- **MDX:** Podcast and posts collections allow `.mdx`; `authors` and `legal` are `.md` only per loader patterns.
